libs.content:
find_library(yamlcpp_libraries
    names  yaml-cpp
    path_suffixes lib64 lib
    hints ${yamlcpp_root})

find_library(sleef_libraries
  names sleef
  path_suffixes lib64 lib
  hints ${sleef_root})

find_library(libxsmm_libraries
  names xsmm
  path_suffixes lib64 lib
  hints ${libxsmm_root})

find_library(libsharp_libfftpack
    names libfftpack libfftpack.a
    path_suffixes lib64 lib
    hints ${libsharp_root})

find_library(libsharp_libraries
    names libsharp libsharp.a
    path_suffixes lib64 lib
    hints ${libsharp_root})

find_library(libsharp_libcutils
    names libc_utils libc_utils.a
    path_suffixes lib64 lib
    hints ${libsharp_root})

find_program(charm_compiler
  names charmc
  path_suffixes bin
  hints ${charm_root} env charm_root
  no_default_path
  doc "the full path to the charm++ compiler 'charmc'"
  )

find_library(scotch_lib
  names scotch
  path_suffixes lib64 lib
  hints ${scotch_root})

find_library(scotch_err_lib
  names scotcherr
  path_suffixes lib64 lib
  hints ${scotch_root})

find_library(tcmalloc_libraries
  names tcmalloc
  path_suffixes lib64 lib
  hints ${tcmalloc_root})

find_library(
    papi_libraries
    
    names libpapi.a papi
    hints ${papi_prefix}/lib ${hiltideps}/lib
)

find_library(googlebenchmark_libraries
    names benchmark
    path_suffixes lib64 lib
    hints ${google_benchmark_root} ${googlebenchmark_root})

find_library(jemalloc_libraries
  names jemalloc
  path_suffixes lib64 lib
  hints ${jemalloc_root})

find_program(
  breathe_apidoc_executable
  names breathe-apidoc
  paths ${breathe_root}
  doc "path to breathe-apidoc executable")

find_library(
  backtrace_lib
  names backtrace
  path_suffixes lib64 lib
  hints ${cmake_cxx_implicit_link_directories})
